this is an awesome tool to monitor process in linux env.
https://forum.hackthebox.com/t/pspy-process-monitoring-cron-job-detection/438

To start it,
>/path/to/pspy
this will also reveal bash history

e.g. /bin/sh -c BORG_PASSPHRASE='xinyVzoH2AnJpRK9sfMgBA' borg delete /opt/borgbackup::usb_1713144873    

make sure to chmod +x permission in victim machine.
